text: Bangalaia duffyi is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1962. It is known from Sierra Leone and the Ivory Coast.BioLib.cz - Bangalaia duffyi. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Prosopocerini Category:Beetles described in 1962
